    "Therefore, we decided to verify the predictive performance of CircDA on HCC (Fig. 4A).",
    "Thirty circRNAs associated with HCC were included in the database, and 15 of the top 20 candidates were confirmed by the literature.Cervical cancer (CC) is the most common gynecological malignancy.",
    "Studies have shown that circRNA plays a vital role in the occurrence of CC.",
    "Figure 4B lists the 20 circRNAs associated with CC with the highest prediction scores.",
    "CircDA predicted 16 out of 18 confirmed cervical cancers."
